            No spam. Unsubscribe anytime. A Txchyon Capital property.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>

      {/* Emergency Roofing Help */}
      <div class="mt-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-2xl border border-red-200 p-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
